DeliveryAcknowledgement DeliveryAcknowledgement Enum

In this Article

Edit

Specifies the different acknowledgement levels for message delivery.

Syntax

Declaration

public enum DeliveryAcknowledgementPublic Enum DeliveryAcknowledgement

Fields

Full
Full

An acknowledgement is sent on delivery success or failure.
NegativeOnly
NegativeOnly

Acknowledgement is sent only if delivery fails.
None
None

Acknowledgement is NOT sent on delivery or failure.
PositiveOnly
PositiveOnly

Acknowledgement is sent only on delivery succeeds.

Details

Namespace

Microsoft.Azure.Devices.Client

Assembly

Microsoft.Azure.Devices.Client.UWP.dll
